title: Mont-de-Marsan
extract:
Mont-de-Marsan is a commune and capital of the Landes department in Aquitaine in southwestern France.


Understand


Get in
RDTL (Régie Départementale des Transports des Landes) provides  regular bus service.


Get around


See
 Donjon Lacataye. The keep of a 14th century castle 
 Despiau-Wlérick Museum. 1930s sculpture by two local artists 


Do
 Stade Montois. The city's rugby and football team.
